=\"rtin-content\" style=\"\">I thoroughly enjoyed courses from here and hope to expand on my gained knowledge about making apps. The courses as well as the examples are well presented, easy to follow and engaging.<\/p>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"rtin-item media\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"pull-left rtin-img\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<img decoding=\"async\" width=\"92\" height=\"92\" src=\"https:\/\/radiustheme.com\/demo\/wordpress\/eikra\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/10\/user9-92x92.jpg\" class=\"img-circle wp-post-image\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/radiustheme.com\/demo\/wordpress\/eikra\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/10\/user9-92x92.jpg 92w, https:\/\/radiustheme.com\/demo\/wordpress\/eikra\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/10\/user9-150x150.jpg 150w, https:\/\/radiustheme.com\/demo\/wordpress\/eikra\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/10\/user9-300x300.jpg 300w, https:\/\/radiustheme.com\/demo\/wordpress\/eikra\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/10\/user9-200x200.jpg 200w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 92px) 100vw, 92px\" \/>\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"media-body rtin-content-area\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<h3 class=\"rtin-title\" style=\"\">Martin Brian<\/h3>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"rtin-designation\" style=\"\">UI Designer<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p class=\"rtin-content\" style=\"\">The courses here exceeded my expectations in many regards, especially in the depth of information supplied. In a very non-threatening environment, I learned key principles of design that I can implement immediately.<\/p>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"rtin-item media\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"pull-left rtin-img\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<img decoding=\"async\" width=\"92\" height=\"92\" src=\"https:\/\/radiustheme.com\/demo\/wordpress\/eikra\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/10\/user8-92x92.jpg\" class=\"img-circle wp-post-image\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/radiustheme.com\/demo\/wordpress\/eikra\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/10\/user8-92x92.jpg 92w, https:\/\/radiustheme.com\/demo\/wordpress\/eikra\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/10\/user8-150x150.jpg 150w, https:\/\/radiustheme.com\/demo\/wordpress\/eikra\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/10\/user8-300x300.jpg 300w, https:\/\/radiustheme.com\/demo\/wordpress\/eikra\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/10\/user8-200x200.jpg 200w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 92px) 100vw, 92px\" \/>\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"media-body rtin-content-area\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<h3 class=\"rtin-title\" style=\"\">David Fahim<\/h3>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"rtin-designation\" style=\"\">Web Developer<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p class=\"rtin-content\" style=\"\">Excellent content and assignments that build on your knowledge, reinforce, and then expand. I recently secured new employment using PHP and couldn&#039;t have done so without the Professional Web Development courses.<\/p>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n<\/div>[\/vc_column][\/vc_row]<\/p>\n<\/section>","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>[vc_row][vc_column][\/vc_column][\/vc_row]<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":0,"parent":0,"menu_order":0,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","template":"","meta":{"footnotes":""},"class_list":["post-1820","page","type-page","status-publish","hentry"],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/radiustheme.com\/demo\/wordpress\/eikra\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/1820","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/radiustheme.com\/demo\/wordpress\/eikra\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/radiustheme.com\/demo\/wordpress\/eikra\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/page"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/radiustheme.com\/demo\/wordpress\/eikra\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/radiustheme.com\/demo\/wordpress\/eikra\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=1820"}],"version-history":[{"count":0,"href":"https:\/\/radiustheme.com\/demo\/